title: New York Robotics launches with 160 startups in its ecosystem
description:
New York Robotics is launching with more than 80 industry partners, 20 academic partners, 40 robotics labs, and over 300 venture capital partners.

The post New York Robotics launches with 160 startups in its ecosystem appeared first on The Robot Report.
